    ### Scaled padding
    By default, all cells have left/right padding which creates a gutter between columns. This 8px padding adjusts to 16px at the large breakpoint.

    ## Vertical Alignment
    By default, cells align top and fill their row vertically. Optionally, whole rows can be configured to align their cells <strong>top</strong> (default), <strong>center</strong>, or <strong>bottom</strong>.
